      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Hamed Ahmadi</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:124px;\"><a href=\"/File:HamedAhmadi.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/d/d8/HamedAhmadi.jpg\" width=\"122\" height=\"153\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:HamedAhmadi.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Hamed Ahmadi <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div>\n<p><b>Hamed Ahmadi</b>,<br />\nan Iranian computer scientist, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Electrical_engineering\">electrical engineer</a>, and lecturer at the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_York\">University of York</a> \nwith previous affiliations at <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Trinity_College_Dublin\">Trinity College Dublin</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_College_Dublin\">University College Dublin</a>, \n<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Beijing_University_of_Technology#Organization\">Beijing Dublin International College</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sheffield_Hallam_University\">Sheffield Hallam University</a> and  <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Essex\">University of Essex</a>.\nHe received a B.Sc. degree in computer software engineering from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ferdowsi_University_of_Mashhad\">Ferdowsi University of Mashhad</a> in 2004, \na  M.Sc. degree in computer engineering from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/National_Aerospace_University_%E2%80%93_Kharkiv_Aviation_Institute\">National Aerospace University of Ukraine</a> in 2008,\nand his Ph.D. in electrical and computer engineering from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/National_University_of_Singapore\">National University of Singapore</a> in 2012 <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>. \nHis research interests include <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_mobile_phone_generations\">next generation of mobile systems</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Self-organizing_network\">self-organizing networks</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Internet_of_things\">internet of things</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mathematical_optimization\">optimization</a>, <a href=\"/Learning\" title=\"Learning\">machine learning</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Game_theory\">game</a> and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Auction_theory\">auction theory</a>, \nand <a href=\"/Genetic_Programming#EvolutionaryAlgorithms\" title=\"Genetic Programming\">evolutionary algorithms</a>. \nIn the early 2000s, he developed an <a href=\"/Othello\" title=\"Othello\">Othello</a> program <b>HamedReversi</b> and the chess program <a href=\"/HamedChess\" title=\"HamedChess\">HamedChess</a>, both still available for download <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>.\nIn 2003, his entry <b>DarwinCaissa</b> applying <a href=\"/Genetic_Programming#GeneticAlgorithm\" title=\"Genetic Programming\">genetic algorithms</a>, became 4th at the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Competitive_programming#Artificial_intelligence_and_machine_learning\">CodeCup</a> 2003 competition <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>, \nplaying the game of Caïssa <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>. \nHis <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alquerque\">Alquerque</a> entry <b>Beta</b> became third at the CodeCup 2008 competition <sup id=\"cite_ref-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Selected_Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Publications</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Hamed_Ahmadi&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-9\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=FnlT7s0AAAAJ&amp;hl=en\">Hani Goodarzi</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Hamed Ahmadi Nejad</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.winston.com/en/who-we-are/professionals/torabi-noori.html\">Noorossadat Torabi</a> (<b>2004</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/15527955/\">On the optimality of the genetic code, with the consideration of termination codons</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/BioSystems\">BioSystems</a>, Vol. 77, Nos. 1-3</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=FnlT7s0AAAAJ&amp;hl=en\">Hani Goodarzi</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=7RluIhUAAAAJ&amp;hl=en\">Hamed Shateri Najafabadi</a>, Kasra Hassani, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Hamed Ahmadi Nejad</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.winston.com/en/who-we-are/professionals/torabi-noori.html\">Noorossadat Torabi</a> (<b>2005</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/15882694/\">On the optimality of the genetic code, with the consideration of coevolution theory by comparison of prominent cost measure matrices</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Journal_of_Theoretical_Biology\">Journal of Theoretical Biology</a>, Vol. 235, No. 3)</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=FnlT7s0AAAAJ&amp;hl=en\">Hani Goodarzi</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=7RluIhUAAAAJ&amp;hl=en\">Hamed Shateri Najafabadi</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Hamed Ahmadi Nejad</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.winston.com/en/who-we-are/professionals/torabi-noori.html\">Noorossadat Torabi</a> (<b>2005</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/16005951/\">The impact of including tRNA content on the optimality of the genetic code</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.scimagojr.com/journalsearch.php?q=13845&amp;tip=sid\">Bulletin of Mathematical Biology</a>, Vol. 67, No. 6</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Hamed Ahmadi</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=-1R8gvQAAAAJ&amp;hl=en\">Mahmoud Reza Hashemi</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.site.uottawa.ca/~shervin/\">Shervin Shirmohammad</a> (<b>2015</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/7396221\">An Open Source Cloud Gaming Testbed Using DirectShow</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.org/db/conf/cloudcom/cloudcom2015.html#AhmadiHS15\">CloudCom 2015</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://hertz.ucd.ie/GianlucaFontanesi.html\">Gianluca Fontanesi</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=BbFxVHMAAAAJ&amp;hl=en\">Anding Zhu</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Hamed Ahmadi</a> (<b>2018</b>). <i>Saving Lives at Sea with UAV-assisted Wireless Networks</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/1809.01030\">arXiv:1809.01030</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=cQRqxEIAAAAJ&amp;hl=en\">Vahid Haghighatdoost</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://scholar.google.ca/citations?user=y1zzy74AAAAJ&amp;hl=en\">Siavash Khorsandi</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Hamed Ahmadi</a>  (<b>2020</b>). <i>Fair Pricing In Heterogeneous Internet of Things Wireless Access Networks Using Crowdsourcing</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2010.04993\">arXiv:2010.04993</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Hamed_Ahmadi&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=76583\">Back to Chess Programming after 20 years</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Hamed Ahmadi</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 14, 2021</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=76599\">Advantage of using bitboard lookup tables to generate moves?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Hamed Ahmadi</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 15, 2021</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Hamed_Ahmadi&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://ahmadihamed.wordpress.com/\">Hamed Ahmadi</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://scholar.google.com.sg/citations?user=lEcMAWwAAAAJ&amp;hl=en\">Hamed Ahmadi‬ - ‪Google Scholar‬</a> </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://hamedahmadi.com/\">Website</a> of <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Hamed Ahmadi</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://hamedahmadi.com/ai_projects.html\">Artificial Intelligence Projects</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Hamed Ahmadi</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://hamedahmadi.com/gametree/\">An Introduction to Game Tree Algorithms</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Hamed Ahmadi</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Hamed_Ahmadi&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://scholar.google.com.sg/citations?user=lEcMAWwAAAAJ&amp;hl=en\">Hamed Ahmadi‬ - ‪Google Scholar‬</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://ahmadihamed.wordpress.com/about-me/\">About me – Hamed Ahmadi</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=76583\">Back to Chess Programming after 20 years</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Hamed Ahmadi</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 14, 2021</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://archive.codecup.nl/2003/competition%3Fcomp%3D4.html\">CodeCup 2003 - Competition</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://archive.codecup.nl/2003/rules_caissa.html\">CodeCup 2003 - Rules of Caissa</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.mindsports.nl/index.php/side-dishes/more-games-by-cf?start=3\">MindSports - Caïssa</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://archive.codecup.nl/2008/35/competition_qcomp_e53.html\">CodeCup 2008 - Competition</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-8\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://hamedahmadi.com/publications.html\">Hamed Ahmadi - Publications</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-9\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.org/pid/10/35.html\">dblp: Hamed Ahmadi</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301150720\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.022 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.024 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 145/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 326/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache